<br>
The surviving eyewitnesses indicate that she was last seen in the Lands of Over Their and that in fierce combat she was abducted by Evil Warlord Phreezin and his forces of Undead Monsters.  No Ransom notes have been received and the worst is assumed.  It is also assumed that she may be mind controlled at this time and unwilling to return.<br>
<br>
The Royal Heartsinger Family offers a Reward of 200 pp Dead and 400 pp alive of the Evil Warlord Phreezin for interrogation and Retribution for any acts he may have commited to our Daughter Rhapsodey Heartsinger.  The Prisoner or body must be Brought to the heartsinger Estates in the Forest of Kelethin to collect the Reward.<br>
<br>
