Oleandra Heartsinger  Sword Mistress of the Elven King <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub51.ezboard.com/bsphereofhonour58352.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kulwein>Kulwein</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Brother of the Sphere</span><br>  Posts: 68<br> <font color=#330000>(12/26/01 6:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/fsphereofhonour58352frm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Villian Wanted Dead.  And Daughter Returned Safely</span><hr size=1> I swear my oath to you and will do everything in my power to see this decree fulfilled, and i am making a force of armed forces, we need a leader, i am but a servant! sound the alarms! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub51.ezboard.com/bsphereofhonour58352.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nellen1>Nellen1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#330000>(12/26/01 6:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/fsphereofhonour58352frm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Why should the unwilling return?</span><hr size=1> Your Royal Majesties,<br>
