<br>
The Wolves of the North will flow out of the barren wastes and over run your pretty little tree city. Kelehtin shall be a burning beacon for anyone on Luclin. Do not interfere with me. My battle prowess is great and my alliances many and strong. <br>
<br>
Be warned ruler of the elves. Leave us be in peace or lose your kingdom.<br>
<br>
